{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"90f9d4c77d","title":"对一篇有关中国领导人的电讯稿的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ae4bbc2513","index":0,"year":1954,"month":3,"day":4,"articleId":"90f9d4c77d"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"af71a4eedb","name":"高岗","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"80410e8a13","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"90f9d4c77d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林彪，当时任人民革命军事委员会副主席、中共中央中南局第一书记。除伯达，当时任中共中央宣传部副部长。胡养木，当时任中共中央宣传部副部长。谭政，当时任中共中央中南局第一副书记。陶铸，当时任中共中央中南局密委、华南分局第四书记。"},{"id":"fba41500a9","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"90f9d4c77d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"高岗，曾任中共中央政治局委员、东北局书记、中央人民政府副主席、国家计划委员会主席。1954年2月，中共七届四中全会揭露了他反党权的阴谋活动。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ab0db7b4bb","type":"title","text":"对一篇有关中国领导人的电讯稿的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"90f9d4c77d"},{"id":"80410e8a13","type":"paragraph","text":"此件送林彪、陈值达、胡乔木、谭政、陶铸五同志一阅。退毛。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"90f9d4c77d"},{"id":"fba41500a9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"90f9d4c77d"},{"id":"f25d57e2cd","type":"paragraph","text":"三月四日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"90f9d4c77d"},{"id":"b93fefce47","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这是毛泽东在合众社1954年2月26日发自东京的一篇电讯上写的三条批语。电讯对毛泽东进出政治舞台的可能性及继示人问题作了推测，其中还谈到对高岗的评价，说高岗“精明”，“曾由于治理满洲有成绩而得到当地领袖们的算敬”。合众社传日本人论高岗”，值得注意。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"90f9d4c77d"},{"id":"46b4a39a96","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"90f9d4c77d"